		"description": "<p>At 3rd level, you can use your psychic abilities to further enhance your senses. While you are psychically focused, you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have blindsight with a range of 30 feet.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on saving throws to disbelieve illusions.</li>\n<li>You have advantage on Perception checks to locate invisible creatures.</li>\n<li>Making ranged weapon attacks at long range does not impose disadvantage on you (you must still abide by a weapon&rsquo;s maximum range).&nbsp;</li>\n<li>You can also ignore half and three-quarters cover when making ranged attacks.&nbsp;</li>\n<li>Non-solid, particulate obstacles like smoke and fog that would normally heavily obscure an area only lightly obscure it for you.</li>\n</ul>",
